ss=\"container-page grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent\">Why Choose Us</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-primary\">Built for trust before speed.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-slate-600\">House Hunt Kisii organizes the rental process around verification, clarity, and direct landlord workflows.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-6 w-6 text-accent\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-semibold text-primary\">Verified landlord signals</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">KYC badges, property statuses, and cleaner inquiry paths help tenants understand who they are speaking to.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-house h-6 w-6 text-accent\"><path d=\"M15 21v-8a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v8\"></path><path d=\"M3 10a2 2 0 0 1 .709-1.528l7-5.999a2 2 0 0 1 2.582 0l7 5.999A2 2 0 0 1 21 10v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-semibold text-primary\">Property-first discovery</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Large imagery, full amenities, and area context keep attention on the home, not random listing noise.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bot h-6 w-6 text-accent\"><path d=\"M12 8V4H8\"></path><rect width=\"16\" height=\"12\" x=\"4\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M2 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 13v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 13v2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-semibold text-primary\">AI-assisted search</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Natural language search helps tenants describe budget, location, family needs, and amenities in plain language.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-6 w-6 text-accent\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-semibold text-primary\">Operational dashboards</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Landlords and admins get focused management surfaces for KYC, listings, payments, and reviews.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-y bg-primary text-white\"><div class=\"container-page\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex items-end justify-between gap-4\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-200\">Latest Properties</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-serif text-4xl font-semibold\">Fresh homes on the market</h2></div><a class=\"items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md text-sm font-semibold transition focus-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border h-11 px-5 hidden border-white/20 bg-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/20 sm:inline-flex\" href=\"/search\"><svg xmlns=\"ht